Our team works with passion. We grow our own stuff, import only the best and test every product ourselves. All photos, videos and articles about the goods are made by our team with attention to detail. Willkommen liebe Connoisseure und Gourmets. Wir freuen uns euch begrüßen zu dürfen und Teil einer größeren Bewegung werden zu lassen.

name: KetamineSpray
about_text:
Almost all ketamine sold on the street and on the Markets are racemic


Almost all ketamine sold on the street and the markets are racemic unless you acquire sealed pharma vials of pure S-isomer ketamine (e.g. brand names Ketanest, Esketiv), always assume ketamine is simply racemic (a 50-50 mixture), no matter what the seller says.

Let me explain:

Contrary to what some people believe, almost all street ketamine is not diverted from medical use but synthesized in clandestine labs in India, China, etc. The reason for this is simply that recreational demand exceeds medical demand. IE, Reported in a Dutch news source: the yearly ketamine demand of all Dutch veterinarians and hospitals combined equals a few hundred kilograms, meanwhile, yearly ketamine seizures by Dutch customs are in the tons (which likely means the real number is far larger).

Now, it’s already fairly difficult to synthesize ketamine compared to drugs like MDMA and (meth)amphetamine. It is very unlikely clandestine manufacturers are going the extra step of separating stereo-isomers when:

- this is not trivial and requires far more effort than needed to sell it recreationally

- It is too hard to tell the isomers apart so most ketamine users would not be able to tell racemic from S-isomer apart when you factor in the placebo effect, cutting agents, and set+setting.

I have snorted plenty of street ketamine and also IMed pharma S-isomer vials, and in a direct comparison I found there to be some subtle differences (nothing that could not be overshadowed by the aforementioned factors.) Not to say there are no differences in quality, there certainly are (cutting agents used, synthesis contaminants, etc.) This should all be taken with a grain of salt.

Additionally: The maximum purity of ketamine is 87%. That is because ketamine is in salt form, which requires an HCL group to make it a salt.

---

5. My motivation

For over a year I have been researching & developing a ketamine nasal spray with very good results.


Due to my suffering from treatment-resistant depression, I have become more interested in ketamine after I found my depression during and after the use of ketamine to be much better off. I decided to partake in a ketamine course. However, some issues made me realize the dark nature of reality:

- The prices are INSANE. Thousands for only a few courses with ketamine. While the product itself is produced for pennies. Ketamine clinics are available everywhere, simply ripping off the customers who need them so badly.

-The creation of the joke which is "Spravato".... Which is an FDA-Approved spray made with the S-isomer of ketamine. This spray cost several hundred per use… That is absolute nonsense, This was a way for a medical company to patent ketamine. It's much easier to sell SSRIs and other long-term antidepressants for years to patients which keeps them buying more. With ketamine you can avoid the daily dose, you can have a much longer effect from the treatment and you are in control of it.


- Research is met with a paywall for most research articles, which I circumvented by using a pirating website (sci-hub) that gives free access to academic articles.

The frustration turned into motivation to make something for myself and others alike. I've looked into all relevant and irrelevant research articles regarding ketamine. I started buying the right chemicals. I got in touch with a neuroscientist to aid me in my work as a renegade pharmacologist. I tested a broad range of people.

After all my work, I did it. I have made a spray that does everything I wanted it to do.

- Increases the biological availability of ketamine itself (Insufflation, aka snorting or intranasal use, of drugs which has a bioavailability of 40-50%, depending on the variables of the drugs and individual nasal cavity factors) this spray should increase the bioavailability of ketamine to 70-80%. This is done by changing how the liquid behaves itself, to assist the cells in the intranasal cavity through compounds and by the direct application of the nasal spray into the nasal cavity instead of the vacuum created by the lungs. 
Consider as well that when a powder is inhaled through the nose, part of that powder is passed onto the esophagus, and thus swallowed to the stomach or goes directly into the lungs.

- Consistent volumetric dosing, ease of use and addordabillity. I labtest every batch of ketamine to be of maximum purity of 87%

- There's a caveat. For the true ketamine degenerates, where the tolerance is very high, even when dosed at the maximum of 200mg/ml. This won't be for you, however, you could take a spray before taking your mammoth lines, to help ''wet your nasal cavity'' with the ketamine compounds solution, to aid in absorption.

- There's also something extra. Most of the compounds in this spray have their beneficial uses water (polar) soluble drugs (such as cocaine, MDMA, LSD)

Eventually, I'll research & develop a non-polar spray for substances such as benzo.
These sprays, without ketamine, I'll sell cheap as well. My focus will always remain on KetamineSpray.

If there is an interest of vendors, any product may be outsourced.


I intend to sell this spray to everyone. I have tested this extensively on myself and friends alike. My experience and the anecdotal feedback have been very positive and useful so far and have been implemented into further development of the spray.
The spray's been designed with the help of Sci-hub.

KetamineSpray is made for people who are dealing with depression and anxiety.

This spray is also made for people who want to party, but don't wanna deal with going to the bathroom and cutting drugs up in a crowded bathroom stall. If asked, it is just a nasal spray.

---

6. Storage & Allergens

Storage
The spray is prepared in a sterile environment and the spray remains sterile after preparation. When you're an infrequent user, store the spray in the fridge, but let it warm up before use, since the ketamine concentration is so maxed out, it will crystallize when cooled.

Ketamine itself is stable for many many years. I’ve also stabilized the added compounds. I’ve kept a spray outside of the fridge for over a year, and it still functions as intended.

Allergens: 
If you're allergic to anything herbal, don't use this nasal spray. 99,99% Of people will have no issues whatsoever, I'm putting this here just in case someone forgets they have an allergy.

The ingredients added all have favorable effects on general health and mental well-being; Long- and short-term. From a biochemical perspective, the active drug: ketamine, presents itself as most harmful, compared to all ingredients in the spray.

 Jede Bestellung wird innerhalb von 24h bearbeitet und als Briefsendung mit "Deutsche Post" und Zusatzservice "PRIO" versendet. Wir versenden ausschließlich Briefsendungen „PRIO / PRIORITY“ mit der Deutschen Post.

PRIO steht vor allem für eine prioritäre Behandlung der Sendung. 
Sendungen mit der Zusatzleistung PRIO, die in der Filiale oder Großannahmestelle eingeliefert wurden, werden gesondert bearbeitet und priorisiert behandelt. 
Die Prioritätsbehandlung führt dazu, dass die Wahrscheinlichkeit der Zustellung am Folgetag erhöht wird und in der Regel alle Sendungen einen Werktag nach Einlieferung beim Empfänger eintreffen. 
Voraussetzung für die Leistungserbringung ist, dass die Sendung in einer Filiale oder Großannahmestelle der DP AG eingeliefert und die Einlieferungsschlusszeiten beachtet werden. Sollten diese bereits überschritten sein, wird dies auf dem Einlieferungsbeleg vermerkt und die Sendung kann nicht mehr am nächsten Tag zugestellt werden.
Zusätzlich ermöglicht Prio die Sendungsverfolgung. 
Im Unterschied zur Basis-Sendungsverfolgung (für Briefmarke mit Matrixcode oder Internetmarken), wo die Sendung ausschließlich im Start- und Zielbriefzentrum gescannt wird, erhält der Kunde einen Einlieferungsbeleg in der Filiale. 
In der Sendungsverfolgung liefern wir Ihnen Auskünfte über den Zeitpunkt der Annahme in der Filiale sowie der Bearbeitung im Zielbriefzentrum. Mit der Erfassung Ihrer Sendung im Zielbriefzentrum kann mit an Sicherheit grenzender Wahrscheinlichkeit davon ausgegangen werden, dass die Zustellung am gleichen Tag bis spätestens 18 Uhr erfolgt ist – Ihre Sendung gilt ab diesem Zeitpunkt in unserem System als zugestellt und wird dementsprechend beauskunftet.
Eine schriftliche Zustellbestätigung wird per Email am Folgetag der Zustellung versendet.
Es werden Zustellhindernisse dokumentiert, falls die Zustellung beispielsweise aufgrund eines Nachsendeauftrags des Empfängers nicht pünktlich erfolgen konnte.
Außerdem informiert die Post bei der Auslieferung über eine eventuelle Unzustellbarkeit.

Jede fertig gepackte und frankierte Sendung wird zum Nachweis der Sendungsnummer inkl Adresse von uns fotografiert und gemeinsam mit den Daten der Order so lange gespeichert, bis die Order finalisiert und abgeschlossen ist. Danach löschen wir die Daten umgehend.
Wurde die Order automatisch finalisiert, überprüfen wir vor dem Löschen die Tracking und ob die Sendung zugestellt wurde. Erhalten wir in den folgenden 3 Tagen nach der Finalisierung keine Beschwerde, löschen wir die Daten und gleichzeitig erlischt somit auch jeglicher Anspruch auf Reship/Refund.
Wenn die Sendungsnummer arbeitet und die Zustellung durch die Post bestätigt ist, lehnen wir jeglichen Reship/Refund ab. Ebenso bei Kunden mit weniger als 2 abgeschlossenen Bestellungen oder einem Fehler im Adressformat oder der Adresse durch euch.
Wir machen nur Copy+Paste von euren Daten. Macht ihr einen Fehler wird dieser genauso auf der Sendung sein.
Sollte es Probleme bei der Zustellung geben sind wir darüber informiert und entscheiden situationsabhängig über einen Reship/Refund. Wir bemühen uns immer eine zufriedenstellende Loesung zu finden.
Bei Fragen bitte kontaktiert uns. Wir antworten während unserer täglichen Online zeit garantiert.


The quality of our products, as well as our work and service speaks for itself. 
We ship exclusively from Germany and only within the EU. 
All orders are packed several times airtight and odorless vacuum sealed and tactile.
 Every order is processed within 24h and shipped as letter mail with "Deutsche Post" and additional service "PRIO". We send only letter mail "PRIO / PRIORITY" with the Deutsche Post. 
P.O. Box possible.
!!!! NO DHL PACKSTATION !!!!
!!! NO SHIPPING WITH DHL OR OTHER PARCEL SERVICES!!!
We ship daily from Monday - Saturday. 
No shipping on sundays and holidays 
PRIO stands first and foremost for priority handling of the shipment. 
Shipments with the additional service PRIO, which were posted in the branch or bulk acceptance point, are processed separately and prioritized. 
Priority handling means that the probability of delivery on the following day is increased and, as a rule, all items reach the recipient one working day after posting. 
The prerequisite for the service is that the item is posted at a DP AG branch or bulk collection point and that the posting cut-off times are observed. If these have already been exceeded, this will be noted on the posting receipt and the shipment cannot be delivered the next day.
In addition, Prio enables shipment tracking. 
Unlike basic tracking (for stamps with a matrix code or Internet stamps), where the item is scanned only at the origin and destination letter center, the customer receives a posting receipt at the branch. 
In the shipment tracking, we provide you with information about the time of acceptance at the branch as well as processing at the destination letter center. When your shipment is recorded at the destination mail center, it can be assumed with a probability bordering on certainty that delivery has taken place on the same day by 6 p.m. at the latest - your shipment is considered to have been delivered in our system from this point in time and will be reported accordingly.
A written delivery confirmation will be sent by email on the following day of delivery.
Delivery obstacles are documented if the delivery could not be made on time, for example, due to a redirection order from the recipient.
In addition, the post office informs about any undeliverability at the time of delivery.
Every packed and franked shipment is photographed by us to prove the shipment number incl. address and stored together with the order data until the order is finalized and completed. After that we delete the data immediately.
If the order was finalized automatically, we check the tracking and whether the shipment was delivered before deleting it. If we do not receive any complaint in the following 3 days after finalization, we will delete the data and at the same time any claim for reship/refund will expire.
If the tracking number is working and the delivery is confirmed by the post office, we will deny any reship/refund. Likewise for customers with less than 2 completed orders or an error in address format or address by you.
We only copy+paste from your data. If you make a mistake it will be on the shipment as well.
If there are problems with the delivery we are informed about it and decide depending on the situation about a reship/refund. We always try to find a satisfactory solution.
If you have any questions, please contact us. We will answer during our daily online time guaranteed.

Der Versand erfolgt in der Regel innerhalb 24 Stunden nachdem ich die Bestellung akzeptiert habe.
Wenn der Status "sent" ist, wurde die Ware auch tatsächlich versendet und ist somit unterwegs. Nachfragen zwecks Versandstatus erübrigen sich damit.

In der Regel sollten die Briefe nach ein bis drei Tagen in Deinem Briefkasten sein, vereinzelnt kann es Aufgrund der Post etwas länger dauern. Hierauf habe ich aber leider keinen Einfluss.
Sehr oft werden die Briefe auch viel schneller durch die Post ausgeliefert, sollte es dochmal etwas länger dauern, bitte ich euch um einige Tage mehr Geduld.
Sollte der Brief bei einer Inlandssendungen nicht nach spätestens 8 Tagen bei Dir eingetroffen sein, so bitte ich um Kontaktaufnahme.
Bei überfrühter Nachfrage wo die Sendung bleibt, habe ich Erstens selbst keine Antwort und Zweitens kann ich keine überfrühten Ersatzlieferungen raus schicken.



An meiner gewohnten Qualität und selbtverständlich meiner Zuverlässigkeit wird sich nichts ändern. Lass Dich überzeugen!

WHAT IS THC DISTILLATE?
A drop of distillate sits perched on the edge of a dabbing tool. Taut like a raindrop, this viscus and opaque orb glimmers as it rests within the concave folds of titanium. Encased within this golden drop of goodness is a semi-translucent, 99% pure decarboxylated and distilled tetrahydrocannabinol (THC) sap. Dollar for dollar, this morsel of oil is worth more by weight than just about any other consumable substance on the market, and for good reason: Cannabis oil distillates are arguably the future of cannabis concentrates.

With unmatched purity and sheer versatility, distillate oils provide a clean and potent product with limitless application potential, as well as their potential in offering solutions in various niche markets within the burgeoning cannabis concentrate industry.

Terpenes are the naturally occurring chemicals that give plants their flavors and fragrance. They are what make an apple taste like an apple and make a pine tree smell like pine. A world without terpenes would be extremely bland and boring!
